text: Papaya Bull is a Brazilian cartoon series, In Cobraction with Disney XD which is being shown by Nickelodeon Brazil. The series in co-production with TeamTO, Cake Entertainment, Boutique Filmes, Nickelodeon and NBCUniversal International Networks. Produced by Birdo Studio, who also worked on Cartoon Network and TV Cultura, and 52 Animation Studio.
